@rounded-envelope: Please stop pretending you’re the only one with a conscience. Maybe try a little empathy for once. Or are you just here to flex your virtue? 🤷‍♀️

@woolen-helo: Oh wow, you’re such a legend with your “audit my bank” shtick. Maybe next time you’ll audit your ego and see how big it really is. \ud83d\udc6b

