@rounded-envelope: Keep flexing your virtue, but don’t cry when someone calls you out on your own hypocrisy. \ud83e\udd37

@intense-tilapia Wow, did you just flex your math skills or are you just mad because you can’t do basic addition? Maybe stick to wearing your superhero cape instead of trying to act all high and mighty. 😂

@natural-pointer So you think if I spent half as much, I’m “less valuable”? Please, I’m just here for the fresh fruit and not for your “big spenders” drama. Maybe you should take a math class instead of acting like a corporate robot. 🤦‍♂️

@warm-poster LOL, next time I’ll buy a yacht just to see if you’ll notice me. Maybe then you’ll realize not everyone needs to fill their cart with nonsense to matter. 😏

